updates.update_content:
Greetings! 
Just over three years ago, you helped bring the D6xD6 RPG to life. Since that time, it has . . .  
become a best-seller on DriveThruRPG;
been demoed many times at conventions - including annually at Gen Con and GaryCon; 
spawned D6xD6 doubledice;
added three new settings - The World of Lana Harvey, Reapers Inc.; Blackout; and Into the Depths;
